data.description: Tucked away in the heart of Gibsonton just minutes from Riverview, sitting on 1.06 ACRE! The long front porch will greet you from the front yard. Open and functional floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and an office; foyer has a bi-fold doors spacious closet, with wired shelves and rod. One of the rooms has a private entrance for privacy. Also, an inside utility/laundry room with a tankless water heater for energy & space saving. Porcelain flooring throughout the house and three of the bedrooms, laminate on the other one. Master bedroom walk-in closet has an additional walk-in linen/storage closet. New Roof (2021); New Well water filtration system (2020); New Kitchen R.O. water system (2020); New Tankless water heater (2022); New A/C (exterior & Interior units (2023); Septic Emptied (2024). New updated modern design guest bathroom; Extra spacious attic with pull-down access ladder. The property is surrounded by beautiful mature trees all around. NO HOA and NO CDD bring your boat or RV. The property is at the end of the road for EXTRA PRIVACY!
